snippet.title: American Truck Simulator: Wyoming DLC
snippet.description:
Home to some of the country's most breathtaking national parks, Wyoming is best known for its red-walled gorges, hot springs, historic prairie towns, pioneer history, and historical attractions.

Add this upcoming ATS map expansion of Wyoming to your Steam wishlist
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1415692/American_Truck_Simulator__Wyoming/
